\"networkQuality\": \"excellent\",\n    \"timeOfDay\": \"10:30\",\n    \"dayOfWeek\": \"Monday\",\n    \"learningModality\": \"individual\",\n    \"environmentalDistractions\": [],\n    \"accessibilityFeatures\": []\n  }\n}"
